Definition: a glandular disorder caused by failure of function of the cortex of the adrenal gland and marked by anemia and prostration with brownish skin
Synonyms: s_disease, s_syndrome, hypoadrenalism, hypoadrenocorticism, glandular_disease, a, glandular, disorder, caused, by, failure, of, function, the, cortex, adrenal, gland, and, marked, anemia, prostration, with, brownish, skin
Category: noun.state
